{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"586690-chao-non-aenuadai","title":"ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?","description":"ເຈົ້າສາມາດນອນຫຼັບດ້ວຍຕາຂ້າງໜື່ງຫຼັບຂ້າງໜື່ງມືນບໍ? ເຈົ້າສາມາດນອນຫຼັບຢູ່ເທິ່ງຕົ້ນໄມ້ບໍ? ປູລາມີຕຽງນອນ, ແຕ່ລາວຢາກຮູ້ວ່າສິ່ງທີ່ມີຊີວິດອື່ນໆນອນແນວໃດ?","language":"Lao","langCode":"lo","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kedsavanh Dalathib","Koulab Yangchaki","Mookda Phengphongsavan","Poukky Vongsena"],"illustrators":["Alex  Latimer"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"The Asia Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/586690-chao-non-aenuadai"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/655698/size3/77f7a8a015fd40eaf3126e2b5f19f654.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/655698/size6/77f7a8a015fd40eaf3126e2b5f19f654.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638263/size6/3fa878f25ded34fc4578c02373e28efc.jpg","text":"ນົກເອີຍ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nຂ້ອຍນອນລັບໃນເວລາທີ່ຂ້ອຍບິນ.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638264/size6/7eb08d9aa5a3c528aaf92828e4613a0e.jpg","text":"ເຈຍເອີຍ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nຂ້ອຍນອນປີ້ນຫົວລົງ.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638265/size6/9dc0eebaf92a25080a219c900e641fa9.jpg","text":"ກົບເອີຍ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nຂ້ອຍນອນຕະແຄງ.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638266/size6/ce7af7050c311f6684329f85eb02bdb3.jpg","text":"ປາມຶກເອີຍ,ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nຂ້ອຍນອນປ່ຽນສີໄປຕາມໃນຄວາມຝັນຂອງຂ້ອຍ.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638267/size6/2b2b83eb3eb33d56ae4d1280f2aedb1d.jpg","text":"ເປັດເອີຍ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nພວກເຮົານອນໂດຍການຜັດປ່ຽນກັນຮັກສາຄວາມປອດໄພ.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638268/size6/aa29ce5816c1ffc017810af13817d430.jpg","text":"ນົກເຄົ້ານ້ອຍເອີຍ,ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nຂ້ອຍນອນຄວ້ຳໜ້າລົງ.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638269/size6/e8163b7b0d23f249f896bc7e43b1eab4.jpg","text":"ນາກນ້ຳເອີຍ,ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nພວກເຮົານອນຈັບມືກັນ.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638270/size6/9c562ee7d4df01f552fd1662a48bd0c4.jpg","text":"ຊ້າງນ້ຳເອີຍ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nຂ້ອຍນອນຢູ່ເທິງບົກ ແລະ ເທິງໜ້ານ້ຳ.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638271/size6/0d37f3f31343988d7b7efcaa9616dcfa.jpg","text":"ຈີຣາຟເອີຍ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nພວກເຮົານອນກອດກັນ","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638272/size6/15d93f23fe1bfce310d86bb5b1531d6b.jpg","text":"ຈອນຟອນເອີຍ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ?\nພວກເຮົານອນເປັນກຸ່ມກອງກັນ.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638723/size6/49d304eb5018f937395052c4c497f88e.jpg","text":"ປູລາ, ເຈົ້ານອນແນວໃດ? ນອນຫຼັບຝັນດີ! ນອນຫຼັບສະໜິດ.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638275/size6/68bbe04286d0837c30471957090ac1c4.jpg","text":"13/14","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/638276/size6/7e44383b91eb556127b354a942ae548a.jpg","text":"14/14","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":13,"words":35}}